      "lineNumber": 5,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "A bare integer literal binds Type to {name:number, kind:int} \u2014 the int\nprimitive is no longer a top-level name; it surfaces as a kind of number.\nPins the architect\u0027s \u0022set %x% = 5 \u2192 {number, int}\u0022 rule end-to-end.",
